# Manual test script

PR test plans should reference relevant items from `docs/MVP-PLAN.md` and, for VMS work, `docs/VMS-FULL-COVERAGE-PLAN.md`.

## Core MVP (every intake/DOCX PR)

- [ ] Admin: sign in, create invite, copy/open link
- [ ] Intake: valid token → upload PDF/DOCX → prefill or manual path
- [ ] Wizard: autosave, back nav, complete → DOCX download
- [ ] Admin: candidate appears (toggle “Show drafts” if still draft)
- [ ] Optional: confirmation email if Resend configured
- [ ] Invalid/expired token blocked

## VMS expansion (when touching parse, wizard fields, or docxBuilder)

- [ ] Parse prefill populates new field groups (`fields_found` reflects manifest groups)
- [ ] Partial parse shows review hint; manual path still completes
- [ ] Gap review blocks submit when required template tags are empty (once implemented)
- [ ] DOCX download: contract template sections populated (test parse-heavy + manual-heavy profiles)
- [ ] `node scripts/test-docx-mapping.mjs` passes
- [ ] After template changes: `node scripts/inventory-template-tags.mjs` reports no unmapped tags

Mark unchecked items when not in scope for the PR.
